# UI / Design system

Single locked theme **"Ombak"**: clean airy neutral surfaces, **teal** brand accent, neutral
charcoal sidebar whose brand mark + active markers pick up the accent, **Plus Jakarta Sans** font
(`@fontsource-variable/plus-jakarta-sans`), `--radius: 0.875rem`. Tokens (OKLch) live in
`apps/web/src/styles/globals.css` — light + dark via `next-themes`. There is **no palette switcher**
(removed); change the accent only by editing `--primary`/`--ring`/`--sidebar-*`.

## Reuse these primitives — don't rebuild
- `components/ui/`: `button card input textarea label select(native, styled) switch popover calendar
  number-input badge skeleton table dialog alert-dialog dropdown-menu tooltip sheet separator tabs
  sonner avatar`.
- `components/`: **`PageHeader`** (`eyebrow`/title/description/`children` actions), **`StatCard`**
  (KPI + tinted icon chip via `tone`, palette `STAT_TONES`), **`EmptyState`**, **`LowStockBadge`**
  (tooltip shows the threshold), **`DateRangePicker`** (single popover, commits on an **Apply**
  button — not on each day click), **`TablePagination`** (rows-per-page select + page nav),
  **`QrImage`** (client PNG QR) + **`QrCodeDialog`** (enlarged, printable label).
- `hooks/`: **`useUrlFilters`** (flat string filters ↔ URL query; defaults dropped),
  **`useDebouncedValue`**, **`usePagination`** (`page`/`pageSize`, resets to 1 on size change;
  `PAGE_SIZE_OPTIONS` 10/20/50/100, `PageMeta`), **`useSoundUnlock`** + **`useScanSoundPref`**
  (scanner beeps via `@/lib/scan-sound`, browser-only + per-station mute).

## Patterns (copy these)
- **List filters**: hold filter state in `useUrlFilters({ ... })`; debounce the search box (300ms)
  via `useDebouncedValue` and push the debounced value into the URL filter; reset `page` to `'1'` on
  any filter change. The page must wrap the client list in `<Suspense>` (it uses `useSearchParams`).
  Reference: `stock-activity.tsx`, `products-dashboard.tsx`, `inventory-overview.tsx`.
- **Pagination**: `const { page, setPage, pageSize, setPageSize } = usePagination()` + render
  `<TablePagination page pageSize total onPageChange onPageSizeChange />` (pass the server `meta.total`
  or the client array length). Reset `page` to 1 when filters change. Server-paginated lists feed `page`/
  `pageSize` into the query (key + params) and read back `{ items, meta }`; client-paginated lists slice
  the fetched array. Reference: `label-studio.tsx`, `po-form.tsx` (server), `inventory-overview.tsx` (client).
- **Forms** (react-hook-form + zod): `<FormLabel required>` adds a red `*`; `<FormDescription>` is a
  small hint with an info icon; numeric fields use `<NumberInput {...field} />` (blank box for 0,
  strips leading zeros); two-column field grids use CSS grid so an error/hint never misaligns the
  columns. Keep create/add forms short; defer advanced settings to an Edit dialog.
- **Row actions**: one primary button (e.g. Adjust) + a `⋯` `DropdownMenu` for the rest; icon-only
  actions get a `Tooltip` (no bare `title`).
- **Toggles**: boolean filters/settings use `<Switch>` + `<Label htmlFor>`, never a toggle-button.
- **Detail pages**: two columns — `lg:grid-cols-3`, main content `lg:col-span-2`, summary/status
  `<aside>` on the right. Cross-module composition stays at the app/page layer.
- **Dynamic inputs**: make dependent choices follow each other (adjust-stock modal: Add/Remove →
  reason options change; live "current → result" preview).
- **Colour variety**: vary KPI/action chips with `STAT_TONES` (primary/amber/rose/sky/violet/emerald)
  — don't render a wall of one colour.
- **Wording**: plain language, no internal jargon ("source of truth" → "accurate/master stock",
  "decrement" → "reduce"). English for now, written to be translatable later.

## Shell & auth
- `components/layout/`: `AppSidebar` (collapses to a 64px **icon rail** via `useUiStore.sidebarOpen`;
  brand mark + a Create menu), `DashboardNavbar` (avatar menu + theme toggle), `SidebarNav`. The
  mobile nav is a `Sheet` themed like the sidebar.
- **Auth is already enforced** (middleware + `authorized()` in `auth.config.ts` → redirect to
  `/login` with `callbackUrl`). Do NOT touch auth config / middleware / cookies without confirming
  (HARD CONSTRAINT #2). The login form already round-trips `callbackUrl`.

## Gotchas
- Production `next build` and `tsx watch server.ts` share `.next` → never build while the dev server
  runs (corrupts the dev session). Stop dev, build, restart.
- `useSearchParams` (incl. via `useUrlFilters`) forces a `<Suspense>` boundary on the page or the
  build errors.
- Typed routes are on: a computed href passed to `router.replace` needs `as Route`.
- Deps added for this system: `geist`, `@fontsource-variable/plus-jakarta-sans`, `react-day-picker`,
  `@radix-ui/react-popover`, `@radix-ui/react-switch`.
